          </h1>
          <p class="text-xl mb-12 max-w-2xl mx-auto text-gray-300">
            Transform your development skills with our comprehensive workshop.
            Learn to build, deploy, and scale AI applications using JavaScript
            and modern tools.
          </p>
          <div
            class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center items-center"
          >
            <a
              href="#register"
              class="bg-yellow-400 text-gray-900 px-8 py-4 rounded-lg text-lg font-semibold hover:bg-yellow-300 transition-colors inline-flex items-center gap-2"
            >
              Join the Workshop <span class="text-xl">‚Üí</span>
            </a>
